{"title":"晒黄花的少女","authors":["刘鸿儒"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":3,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"晒黄花的少女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘鸿儒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山野敞开成熟的胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敞开藏不住的色彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农家铺着凉席的屋顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位少女在晾晒黄花菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把心中金色的秘密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和金色的收获一同摊开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟拂动她的秀发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光顺脸颊流下来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她忙着用无数根“金针”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝好曾被撕烂了的云彩。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}